text:
="preserve">Yairus Gwijangge (31 December 1968 – 15 November 2020) was an Indonesian politician. He was born in Mapenduma, Papua, Indonesia. Gwijiangge was the Regent of Nduga from 2011 to 2016 and again from 2017 until his death.
Gwijangge died on 15 November 2020 at a hospital in Jakarta, aged 51.
